            services, management of the loyalty programmes (Taj InnerCircle, Taj Advantage 
            Plus, TAPP Me etc), mass mailings, for which it is necessary to provide personal 
            information. These parties are contractually prohibited from using the personal 
            information for any purpose other than those specified by IHCL. We may provide 
